{"tid":56383,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"大阪周遊卡","createTime":"2016-12-27T08:04:39.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-27T20:41:06.000Z","uid":44427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e3d28a055debee3d8415dc178cd93d3354f8f40c","tid":56383,"uid":44427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T08:04:39.000Z","msg":"跟唔跟日本周遊卡官網行程咁行好?<br />\n有無巴絲有推薦,邊啲係必去<br />\n利申:幾個男人一月去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d221d2928648819fc0f6a768672a0e1b73fa9c4","tid":56383,"uid":21861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T08:11:10.000Z","msg":"上次跟左大部分，好多景點唔洗錢幾底玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd9d79aa0cb77fc03e1a19d0810f7eef0eb69ee2","tid":56383,"uid":44427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T08:11:39.000Z","msg":"我知空中庭園,動物園一定會去"},{"pid":"c1fc1b4dc6508286816daed292dee2c492f3f52b","tid":56383,"uid":17812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T08:12:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我知空中庭園,動物園一定會去</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n動物園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"714ec430d3f79638a6d5d8e6ec5de85f7f02e7f2","tid":56383,"uid":44427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T08:15:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我知空中庭園,動物園一定會去</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n動物園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有伏?定點?<br />\n其實我見周遊卡好多都係博物館,美術館同水上船...係咪買一日卡都夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a8e20f5b6dfa8ae56f5dcad7c998ed7c96a0f91","tid":56383,"uid":66954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T08:24:40.000Z","msg":"同阿媽去，<br />\n去咗梅田夜景，santa maria坐船，摩天輪，今昔館 (租和服500yen)<br />\n<br />\n唔係陪阿媽我唔會去呢d景點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b5b0e957ec2e0c5c4fcc61a642a3b8f765ee961","tid":56383,"uid":66111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T08:25:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我知空中庭園,動物園一定會去</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n動物園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有伏?定點?<br />\n其實我見周遊卡好多都係博物館,美術館同水上船...係咪買一日卡都夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n印象中一日同兩日都好似唔係差好遠價錢<br />\n仲有張卡包埋地鐵  緊係兩日啦"},{"pid":"8423ba7df1ab3390e5e7f9bd0c6083f1730d1071","tid":56383,"uid":66111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T08:27:43.000Z","msg":"動物園係唔錯既 幾多野睇<br />\n<br />\n有北極熊睇，不過見佢好慘咁應該好熱<br />\n<br />\n免費黎講唔去真係曬左"},{"pid":"ad5a8072c38df7f413acd8551fec9339356017f2","tid":56383,"uid":24324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T08:27:53.000Z","msg":"上次去左大坂城通天塔動物園摩天輪空中庭園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2595e5b5b2e3557842e62468f908f4a10f868f14","tid":56383,"uid":19310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T08:48:54.000Z","msg":"今昔館/大阪城/梅田空中庭園/hepfive摩天輪/天保山摩天輪/santa maria個人認為最好去晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cc0f58080e58eca2e7907e0f40e8ecf24bbe74c","tid":56383,"uid":33727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T09:08:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>跟唔跟日本周遊卡官網行程咁行好?<br />\n有無巴絲有推薦,邊啲係必去<br />\n利申:幾個男人一月去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n買兩日券，連續兩晚去浸溫泉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa9d3f10e08090d048f564313f35fe891d3a51c0","tid":56383,"uid":31629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T09:41:40.000Z","msg":"諗起幾個男人一月去空中庭園凍到仆街攬埋一舊個畫面 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再望下隔離對一男一女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae5457acdb22bcf78838f3e9f6854f35d76f2892","tid":56383,"uid":807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T20:41:06.000Z","msg":"留意返一日券同兩日券適用範圍唔一樣"}]}